module.description.mathaxlegacy.auto-ez: Announces in chat when you kill someone.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.better-c: Improves your chat experience in various ways.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.chat-bot: Bot which automatically responds to commands.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.message-: Sends a specified message to any player that enters render distance.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.anchor-a: Automatically places and breaks Respawn Anchors to harm entities.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.anti-anc: Automatically prevents Anchor Aura by placing a slab on your head.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.anti-anv: Automatically prevents Auto Anvil by placing between you and the anvil.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.anti-bed: Places string to prevent beds being placed on you.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.arrow-do: Tries to dodge arrows coming at you.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.auto-32k: Automatically attacks other players with a 32k weapon.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.auto-anv: Automatically places anvils above players to destroy helmets or get out of the hole (Burrow patched servers).
module.description.mathaxlegacy.auto-cit: Automatically cities a target by mining the nearest obsidian next to them.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.auto-log: Automatically disconnects you when certain requirements are met.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.auto-tot: Automatically equips a totem in your offhand.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.auto-tra: Traps people in an obsidian box to prevent them from moving.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.auto-wea: Finds the best weapon to use in your hotbar.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.auto-web: Automatically places webs on other players.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.bed-aura: Automatically places and explodes beds in the Nether and End.
Automatically places and explodes beds in the Nether and End.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.bow-aimb: Automatically aims your bow for you.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.burrow: Attempts to clip you into a block.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.cev-brea: Places obsidian on top of people and explodes crystals on top of their heads after destroying the obsidian.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.critical: Performs critical attacks when you hit your target.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.insta-au: Automatically instamines the closest city block.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.offhand: Allows you to hold specified items in your offhand.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.piston-a: Moves crystals into people using pistons and explodes them.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.self-anv: Automatically places an anvil on you to prevent other players from going into your hole.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.smart-su: Attempts to save you from crystals automatically.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.surround: Surrounds you in blocks to prevent you from taking lots of damage.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.capes: When enabled you will see MatHax capes on users which have them.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.spin-bot: Makes you spin like Spin Bot in CS:GO.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.swarm: Allows you to control multiple instances of MatHax from one central host.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.anti-pac: Attempts to prevent you from being disconnected by large packets.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.auto-mou: Automatically does the mount bypass dupe.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.auto-rec: Automatically reconnects when disconnected from a server.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.better-t: Various improvements to the tab list.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.coordina: Logs coordinates of various events. Doesn't work on Spigot/Paper servers.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.middle-c: Lets you use items when you middle click.
Adds or removes a player as a friend using middle click.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.offhand-: An exploit that can crash other players by swapping back and forth between your main hand and offhand.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.packet-c: Allows you to cancel certain packets.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.tps-sync: Syncs the clients TPS with the server's.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.vanilla-: When connecting to a server it spoofs the client name to be 'vanilla'.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.air-jump: Lets you jump in the air.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.anchor: Helps you get into holes by stopping your movement completely over a hole.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.anti-afk: Performs different actions to prevent getting kicked for AFK reasons.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.anti-lev: Prevents the levitation effect from working.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.anti-voi: Attempts to prevent you from falling into the void.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.blink: Allows you to essentially teleport while suspending motion updates.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.boat-fly: Transforms your boat into a plane.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.click-tp: Teleports you to the block you click on.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.elytra-f: Gives you more control over your elytra.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.elytra-b: Boosts your elytra as if you used a firework.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.entity-c: Lets you control rideable entities without a saddle.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.entity-s: Makes you go faster when riding entities.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.flight: FLYYYyy! No Fall is recommended with this module.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.gui-move: Allows you to perform various actions while in GUIs.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.high-jum: Makes you jump higher than normal.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.jesus: Walk on liquids and powder snow like Jesus.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.no-fall: Attempts to prevent you from taking fall damage.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.no-slow: Allows you to move normally when using objects that will slow you.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.packet-f: Allows you to fly using packets.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.parkour: Automatically jumps at the edges of blocks.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.phase: Lets you clip through ground sometimes.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.reverse-: Allows you to fall down blocks at a greater speed.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.safe-wal: Prevents you from walking off blocks or on blocks that you dont want.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.speed: Modifies your movement speed when moving.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.spider: Allows you to climb walls like a spider.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.step: Allows you to walk up full blocks instantly.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.trident-: Boosts you when using riptide with a trident.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.velocity: Prevents you from being moved by external forces.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.anti-spa: Protects the player from losing the respawn point.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.auto-men: Automatically replaces items in your offhand with mending when fully repaired.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.auto-rep: Automatically refills items in your hotbar, main hand, or offhand.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.auto-too: Automatically switches to the most effective tool when performing an action.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.chest-sw: Automatically swaps between a chestplate and an elytra.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.exp-thro: Automatically throws XP bottles in your hotbar.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.fast-use: Allows you to use items at very high speeds.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.liquid-i: Allows you to interact with liquids.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.no-break: Completely removes the delay between breaking blocks.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.no-inter: Blocks interactions with certain types of inputs.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.no-minin: Allows you to mine blocks through entities.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.no-rotat: Attempts to block rotations sent from server to client.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.portals: Allows you to use GUIs normally while in a Nether Portal.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.potion-s: Stops potion effects ticking when you stand still.
Spoofs specified potion effects for you. SOME effects DO NOT work.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.speed-mi: Allows you to quickly mine blocks.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.backgrou: Custom background when in GUI screens.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.better-t: Displays more useful tooltips for certain items.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.block-se: Modifies how your block selection is rendered.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.boss-sta: Stacks boss bars to make your HUD less cluttered.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.breadcru: Displays a trail behind where you have walked.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.break-in: Renders the progress of a block being broken.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.camera-t: Allows modification of the third person camera.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.city-esp: Displays blocks that can be broken in order to city another player.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.custom-c: Allows you to customize your crosshair.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.custom-f: Allows your FOV to be more customizable.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.entity-o: Displays the name of the player who owns the entity you're looking at.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.fake-pla: Spawns a client-side fake player for testing usages.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.freecam: Allows the camera to move away from the player.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.free-loo: Allows more rotation options in third person.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.hand-vie: Alters the way items are rendered in your hands.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.hole-esp: Displays holes that you will take less damage in. Useful in cpvp.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.item-hig: Highlights selected items when in guis.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.item-phy: Applies physics to items on the ground.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.light-ov: Shows blocks where mobs can spawn.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.logout-s: Displays a box where another player has logged out at.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.new-chun: Detects completely new chunks using certain traits of them
module.description.mathaxlegacy.no-rende: Disables certain animations or overlays from rendering.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.time-cha: Makes you able to set a custom time.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.tracers: Displays tracer lines to specified entities.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.trail: Renders a customizable trail behind your player.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.trajecto: Predicts the trajectory of throwable items.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.unfocuse: Will not render anything when your Minecraft window is not focused.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.void-esp: Renders holes in bedrock layers that lead to the void.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.xray: Only renders specified blocks. Good for mining.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.air-plac: Places a block where your crosshair is pointing at.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.ambience: Change the color of various pieces of the environment.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.anti-cac: Prevents you from taking damage from cacti.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.auto-nam: Automatically uses nametags on entities without a nametag. WILL nametag ALL entities in the specified distance.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.auto-sme: Automatically smelts items from your inventory
module.description.mathaxlegacy.build-he: Allows you to interact with objects at the build limit.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.color-si: Allows you to use colors on signs on NON-PAPER servers. (use "&" for color symbols)
module.description.mathaxlegacy.echest-f: Places and breaks EChests to farm obsidian.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.enderman: Either looks at all Endermen or prevents you from looking at Endermen.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.flamethr: Ignites every alive piece of food.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.infinity: Allows you to essentially mine forever.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.liquid-f: Places blocks inside of liquid source blocks within range of you.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.mount-by: Allows you to bypass the IllegalStack plugin and put chests on entities.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.packet-m: Sends packets to mine blocks without the mining animation.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.stash-fi: Searches loaded chunks for storage blocks. Saves to <your minecraft folder>/MatHax/Legacy/Stashes folder.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.timer: Changes the speed of everything in your game.
module.description.mathaxlegacy.vein-min: Mines all nearby blocks with this type.
